text: Cree Elizabeth Cicchino (born 9 May 2002) is an American actor. She began her career as a child actor playing one of the lead roles, Babe Carano, on the Nickelodeon comedy television show Game Shakers. She then went on to play Marisol Fuentes on the Netflix comedy television show Mr. Iglesias, and to play Mim in the 2020 Netflix movie The Sleepover. == References == Category:2002 births Category:Actors from New York City Category:Living people Category:American child actors Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors
